# Secret environment for the reference-delivery example.
#
# Copy to `secrets/.env` (gitignored) only when the selected Smith coding agent
# or another operator-provided agent command needs provider/auth environment
# variables. The launcher sources this file before starting the single
# smith-worker, so the agent process inherits these variables from the worker.
#
# The Forgejo webhook secret is generated automatically in `secrets/webhook-secret`
# and the provisioner writes per-role Forgejo credentials to `secrets/roles.env`;
# do not paste those generated credentials here.
#
# Examples (uncomment only the secrets your selected agent actually needs):
#
# export OPENAI_API_KEY=...
# export ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=...
# export SMITH_PROVIDER_SECRET=...
